Nutrient data for: CADBURY BOOST CHOCOLATE BAR 68 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210212573
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK, sugar, vegetable fats (palm, shea), glucose syrup, dextrose, skimmed MILK powder, cocoa butter, cocoa mass, whey powder (from MILK), WHEAT flour (with added calcium, iron, niacin and thiamin), fat-reduced cocoa powder, humectant (glycerol), emulsifiers (E442, E471, sunflower lecithin), flavourings, dried cellulose, salt, BARLEY malt syrup, raising agent (sodium hydrogen carbonate), tartaric acid. MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 14% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN PEANUTS, SOYA. Date available: 05/09/2018 Date last updated by company: 05/09/2018
